    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2011 Porsche Cayman S, a pinnacle of mid-engine balance. This 987.2 iteration features the coveted 3.4L DFI flat-six, delivering linear power delivery without the IMS concerns of its predecessor. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle with a factory short-shifter, the mechanical engagement is unparalleled. The chassis remains factory-spec, benefitting from Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a mechanical locking rear differential. Zero bore scoring, pristine underbody, and original factory paint with consistent mic readings. This is a collector-quality example with a documented service history, ready for the most discerning enthusiast.",
