    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This car has been climate-control garaged since day one, and the care reflects in every detail. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-fresh luster without a single swirl mark, scratch, or stone chip. Inside, the premium leather seats remain supple and firm, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, dial, and technological feature functions flawlessly, exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; it comes with a complete, meticulously documented service history from the original dealership, with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage remains as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved specimen that looks, feels, and drives like it just left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
