    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally babied, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
