    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, maintained to an exacting standard. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through its individual throttle bodies with a double VANOS system that operates within factory tolerances. The six-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise gate selection, free of synchro wear, transmitting power to a tight limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe mounting points have been inspected and remain structurally pristine. The suspension retains its original geometry and damping characteristics, providing the communicative feedback and lateral stability synonymous with the M-chassis. All seals, bushings, and fluid lines are supple and leak-free, making this a mechanically transparent example for the discerning enthusiast.",
